claim: Tommy Chong has Canadian and American citizenship.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Thomas B. Kin Chong  (  born May 24 , 1938  )  is a Canadian-American comedian and actor , who is known for his marijuana-themed Cheech & Chong comedy albums and movies with Cheech Marin , as well as playing the character Leo on Fox 's That '70s Show .
